<h3>People</h3>
I feel very lucky in my life that know some wonderful people.  
Unfortunately none of them come to mind right now.  Anyhow, here are
<!WA1><a href="http://www.cs.unm.edu/~dsmith/people-to-know.html">some losers</a>
who I don't actually know, and who I would not really want to be associated
with, but well, check it out.  Maybe.
<p>
